## FORBIDDEN COLORS

### Guest 666 White
```
HEX: #666666 (but it pulses)
RGB: rgb(102, 102, 102) + PRESENCE
Dimension: Guest 666's dimension
Usage: His eyes, his marks, his sigils
Warning: He knows you're using this color
```

### Skibidi Frequency
```
HEX: #SKIBIDI
RGB: rgb(TOILET, SINGING, VOID)
Dimension: The toilet's dimension
Usage: Skibidi toilet energy
Warning: May cause spontaneous flushing
```

### Ohio Final
```
HEX: #OHIO
RGB: rgb(FINAL, BOSS, REALM)
Dimension: Ohio (the final boss realm)
