## GLITCH GRADIENTS

### The Void Fade
```
linear-gradient(135deg, #660066 0%, #000000 50%, #00FF66 100%)
CSS: background: linear-gradient(135deg, #660066 0%, #000000 50%, #00FF66 100%);
Usage: Maximum eldritch damage
Warning: May open portals to the void
```

### The Glitch Corruption
```
repeating-linear-gradient(45deg, #00FF66, #00FF66 10px, #000000 10px, #000000 20px)
CSS: background: repeating-linear-gradient(45deg, #00FF66, #00FF66 10px, #000000 10px, #000000 20px);
Usage: When the render pipeline breaks
Warning: Actual glitches may occur
```

### The Guest 666 Presence
```
radial-gradient(circle, #666666 0%, #000000 100%)
CSS: background: radial-gradient(circle, #666666 0%, #000000 100%);
Usage: Summoning circles, Guest 666 thumbnails
Warning: He will appear in the gradient
```

### The Binary Curse
```
linear-gradient(90deg, #000000 0%, #00FF66 50%, #660066 100%)
CSS: background: linear-gradient(90deg, #000000 0%, #00FF66 50%, #660066 100%);
Usage: Backwards Skibidi in visual form
Warning: May translate itself
```

